  "body_text_preview": "Home\nSchedule\nTasks\nCharts\nMessages\nReports\n Help \nWill Demo\nWill Demo Practice\n Lock\n Settings\n Log out\nDashboard\n \nDocuments\n \nDirectory\nPractice dashboard\n PRACTICE SETUP\n16%\nYour practice. Our purpose.\n\nSubscribe to the Practice Fusion EHR, the leading cloud-based EHR for small practice physicians.\n\nBuy a subscription\nINCOMPLETE\nEHR users\n\nYour EHR system will improve with more users\n\nVideo tutorial\nAdd your users\nINCOMPLETE\nLabs\n\nSend orders and receive results in your EHR\n\nVideo tutorial\nAdd your labs\nINCOMPLETE\nImaging centers\n\nImages and reports viewed in your EHR\n\nVideo tutorial\nConnect imaging centers\nINCOMPLETE\ne-Prescribing\n\nSend prescriptions directly to a patient's preferred pharmacy\n\nVideo tutorial\nSet up e-Prescribing\nCPT codes license access\n\nGet access to CPT code sets by purchasing a license from Optum360, an AMA authorized distributor\n\nLearn more\nBilling\n\nCreate and send superbills from your EHR\n\nVideo tutorial\nExplore billing solutions\nInsurance eligibility\n\nInsurance eligibility is available for your practice, click here to learn more\n\nSettings\n\nManage personal and practice-level settings\n\nCustomer support\n\nLearn about popular topics, and find resources for your practice\n\nINCOMPLETE\nDirect Messaging\n\nRegister your unique Direct address\n\nSet up Direct messaging\nTemplate community\n\nFind, rate, and share charting templates with the community\n\nINCOMPLETE\nPractice Fusion Billing Services\n\nOptimize your practice's revenue and ease medical billing tasks\u2014upgrade your subscription today.\n\nLearn more\nVeradigm programs\n\nConnect to a range of programs for your EHR through the Veradigm portal\n\nApp Marketplace\n\nAdd new apps, and manage existing authorized apps\n\nOpen App Marketplace\nIntegrated Patient Payment Solution\n\nSimplify payment collection with TrustCommerce for a smooth, secure, and integrated experience.\n\nTelehealth\n\